     /msg NickServ REGISTER pass user@example.com
     >> SEE your mailbox
     /msg NickServ VERIFY REGISTER user xxxxxxxxxxxx

  Save windows layout
     /layout save

  Ignore crap beside choosen channels
     /ignore * joins parts quits
     /ignore -except #suckless,#radare joins parts quits

